Class SocialDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • cmput301f17t13.com.catisadog.utils.data.DataSource<User>
        • cmput301f17t13.com.catisadog.models.followrequest.SocialDataSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Repository.OnResultListener<User>, com.google.firebase.database.ValueEventListener

    public class SocialDataSource
extends DataSource<User>
implements com.google.firebase.database.ValueEventListener, Repository.OnResultListener<User>
    This is a data source for the list of User that the CurrentUser is following or the list of User that are followers of the CurrentUser. This is achieved by listening on the FollowRequest items related to the current user and then fetching the individual User objects.
